thread.title: Thomas Neff

author: Thomas Neff
title: Thomas Neff
text: This was the first time I have used this service from Amazon. I was pleasantly surprised to discover this retailer. They have a wide selection of equipment and I will order from them again. I usually order from Cabela's or Bass Pro Shop. But why should people on the East Coast have all the access and the fun of ordering from this retailer. Prices are competitive.
